metadata.name: Gaia
metadata.description: Gaia is The ancestral mother of all life and formed from a complex language of predator and prey, of growth and dormancy, birth and migration, seasonal change, storms, currents, and finally, of death and necessity. However, with time as all mothers she changed under influence of her children. Now the metal and mechanisms surround her body. Ancient eyes are burning with billions of factories. and looking in infinite cosmos for new horizons her children will conquer soon.
